Title: Veet Full Body Waxing Kit (Sensitive Skin)
Description: Waxing at home can be a simple and mess-free affair if you do so with this pack of Veet full body waxing kit. Ideal for Sensitive skin Enriched with the nourishing goodness of ingredients like Almond Oil and Vitamin E, each waxing strip in this packet contains nutrients that are essential for sensitive skin. Easy Grip Tabs The tabs of these waxing strips allow a firm hold, so you can effectively pull out even the most stubborn hair from the roots. One waxing session will keep your skin smooth and exfoliated for up to 4 weeks. With regular use, your hair starts to become softer, thinner, and finer. How To Use: Step 1 - Rub the wax strip between your hands so its easy to separate. Step 2 - Test the product on your legs before moving on to sensitive areas like your underarms and bikini line, if its your first experience with waxing. For use on the underarm, cut the strips into suitable sizes and make the area taunt by lifting your elbow up. Place the strips in different directions, keeping in mind the opposite directions in which hair on the upper and lower part of the underarm grow. For use on the bikini line, cut the strips into suitable sizes and be sure to only use on small areas at a time. For best results: Thoroughly wash your skin with soap and water before waxing. Pull back the wax strip against the direction of hair growth, to completely uproot them. The wax strips can be reused until they lose their stickiness. Precautions: 1. Please read and retain the outer packaging that has full precautions and directions for use. 2. This product is suitable for use on legs, arms, underarms and bikini line. 3. This product is NOT suitable for use on the head, face, eyes, nose, ears, around the anus, genitals and nipples. 4. Do not use this product on varicose veins, scars, moles, spotty, broken, irritated or sunburnt skin. Avoid use if your skin has had an adverse reaction to waxing in the past. 5. Please give a gap of at least 72 hours between hair removal sessions. 6.Hair should be between 2mm and 5mm long for you to have a comfortable waxing session. You can trim the hair with scissors before waxing if its longer. 7. If you are taking medication which can affect skin, or if you suffer from any skin-related disorder, please consult your doctor before using this product. 8. Before every use, test your skins reaction to the product by using it on a small area. If there is no adverse reaction after 24 hours, you may continue to use it. 9. If you experience any smarting/tingling sensation while using the product, remove it immediately and rinse thoroughly with cold water. If a burning sensation persists, please seek medical advice. 10. Avoid scratching the skin where the product has been used. 11. Please wait 24 hours before using antiperspirants, perfumed products and artificial tanning equipment, or swimming or sunbathing. 12. Please keep the product out of reach of children. In case of ingestion, please seek immediate medical advice and produce the outer packaging of the product. 13. The product should not come in contact with eyes, but if it does, rinse with plenty of water and seek medical advice immediately.
